Next-Gen Futures Order System Contract
Objective: Develop a Solidity contract for managing advanced futures orders.
Key Features:
Support for various complex futures orders, like limit and stop orders.
Real-time integration with diverse market price feeds.
Automated processes for order fulfillment and dispute resolution.
Detailed transaction logs for compliance.
Expanded Scope: Include exotic futures contracts (weather derivatives, prediction markets).
Innovative Feature: Use machine learning to predict market trends and adjust orders.
Creative Interpretation: Design unique risk management tools within the contract.
Expected Deliverable: A deployable, well-documented Solidity contract with user guides.
